| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1782 — Recovery Inhibition (bqtlock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 75f1ef96-d973-556c-85ba-bf81bf3477ca"
